---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'The One-Day Coherence Intensive | The Coherence Co.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-56 pb-24">

    <!-- ─── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
      The One-Day Coherence Intensive
    </h1>
    <p class="text-primary font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
      For executives and leaders seeking balance in their organizations
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      A guided diagnostic experience where you'll map your organization's Coherence Index, identify your Narrative Debt, and build a 30-day protocol you can implement immediately.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-white font-semibold max-w-3xl mb-16">
      This isn't a seminar. It's a working session.
    </p>

    <!-- ─── Typical Journey ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">The Typical Journey</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">87% of organizations that complete the One-Day Intensive request ongoing stewardship within 60 days. Here's why:</p>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">The Intensive gives you the diagnostic and the 30-day protocol. That solves the immediate crisis. But Coherence isn't a project—it's a practice. Most executive teams realize they need:</p>
      <ul class="list-none mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li class="text-slate-300 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary">Quarterly Coherence Audits to track drift and recalibrate</li>
        <li class="text-slate-300 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary">Ongoing steward access for real-time guidance during high-stakes decisions</li>
        <li class="text-slate-300 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary">Custom protocol design as the organization evolves</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">We offer retainer-based stewardship for organizations committed to long-term coherence. Pricing starts at $15K/quarter for up to 20 leaders. Most clients stay engaged for 18–24 months as the practice embeds into culture.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-300">You don't have to commit to this now. But 9 out of 10 do after seeing the results of the first 30 days.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── Three Cards ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-white/10 border border-white/10 mb-16">

      <!-- The Experience -->
      <div class="bg-[#0f1623] p-10 flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The Experience</h3>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Morning: Diagnosis</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Apply the Coherence Canvas to your actual organization in real-time</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Map where pace has outrun comprehension in your team</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Identify your three highest-leverage intervention points</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Measure your baseline Coherence Index</li>
        </ul>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Afternoon: Design</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Build your Decision Pacing Protocol</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Design Temporal Buffers that fit your calendar</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Create Trust Infrastructure checkpoints for your leadership team</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Draft your 30-day implementation roadmap</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- The Outcomes -->
      <div class="bg-[#0f1623] p-10 flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The Outcomes</h3>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">What You Leave With</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Your completed Coherence Canvas with organization-specific diagnostics</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">A 30-day implementation protocol ready to deploy Monday morning</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Membership in the Coherence Community with ongoing peer support</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Certification of Completion recognizing your commitment to temporal stewardship</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Quantified baseline of your Coherence Index to measure progress against</li>
        </ul>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Throughout the Day</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Work alongside a small group of peer executives facing similar challenges</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Catered lunch designed for conversation and reflection</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Guided facilitation by certified Coherence stewards</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Real-time feedback on your specific organizational dynamics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Who Should Attend -->
      <div class="bg-[#0f1623] p-10 flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Who Should Attend</h3>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">C-suite executives moving faster than their teams can integrate</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Leaders who sense misalignment but can't name it</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Organizations scaling rapidly and losing momentum</li>
          <li class="text-slate-300 text-sm pl-4 relative before:content-['•'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-primary">Teams caught between urgency and understanding</li>
        </ul>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Who This Isn't For</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-3">If you're looking for a quick fix, this won't work. Coherence takes 30–90 days to embed. If you need results by next Tuesday, hire a consultant.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-3">If your organization is under 20 people, you don't need this yet. Below that threshold, most issues are communication, not systemic coherence.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-3">If you're not willing to change your calendar, don't come. The Decision Pacing Protocol requires non-negotiable buffers.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-8">If you're looking for external validation, we're not therapists. We diagnose systems and build protocols.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm italic">Not ready to commit? <a href="/contact" class="text-primary font-bold no-underline hover:underline">Start with the 5-minute Coherence Assessment</a> to see your baseline score first.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── Risk Reversal ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-12 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-8">Why This Is the Safest Decision You'll Make This Quarter</h2>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">You Don't Pay Until You Know It's Right</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8">Start with the 5-minute Coherence Assessment. Free. No email required. You'll see your baseline score immediately. If it resonates, book a 15-minute call. If that call doesn't convince you, you've lost 20 minutes. That's the risk.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">The Intensive Comes with a No-Confusion Guarantee</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8">If you attend the full day and leave thinking "this didn't apply to my situation," we refund 100% of your investment. No questions, no hard feelings. We've never had to invoke this—but it's there because your time matters more than our revenue.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Try It in Your Organization for 30 Days First</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8">Not ready for the full intensive? Pilot the Decision Pacing Protocol with your leadership team for 30 days. We'll give you the implementation guide, a baseline Coherence Index measurement, and a check-in call at day 15. $2,500. If it doesn't measurably improve decision velocity, we refund it and you keep the framework.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Everything Stays Confidential—In Writing</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300">We sign NDAs. We never reference your company, your challenges, or your data. Ever. Not in case studies, not in testimonials, not in other client conversations. The only public record is that you worked with us—and only if you approve it.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── Logistics ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">

        <div>
          <h5 class="font-heading text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/10 pb-3 mb-6">Upcoming Schedule</h5>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3">
              <strong class="text-white text-sm">Q1 2026</strong>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Denver</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3">
              <strong class="text-white text-sm">Q2 2026</strong>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Chicago</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3">
              <strong class="text-white text-sm">Q3 2026</strong>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Austin</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3">
              <strong class="text-white text-sm">Q4 2026</strong>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">San Francisco</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm"><strong class="text-white">Time:</strong> 9:00 AM – 4:30 PM (includes catered lunch and breaks)</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h5 class="font-heading text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/10 pb-3 mb-6">Investment & Options</h5>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4"><strong class="text-white">Pricing:</strong> Varies by location | Group pricing available for leadership teams</p>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-8"><strong class="text-white">On-Premise:</strong> Bring the Intensive to your organization. Custom pricing for teams of 8–20 leaders.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-6 py-4 hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
              Reserve Your Seat
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-white/30 text-white text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-6 py-4 hover:border-white transition-colors">
              Request On-Premise Pricing
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>